Rq
	At route /
		System default page
		Set a default page. System default page is loaded only if default page is missing
	Load all apps to applist

	If there was an app running,
		start that app,
	otherwise 
		if default app is set
			start default app
		otherwise
			wait for user to start the app s/he wants to use

			app can have default page or not(in which case default page or system default page reigns as may be the case)